      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·豳風·006.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">九罭.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九罭之魚，鱒魴。我覯之子，袞衣繡裳。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the net with its nine bags
Are rud and bream.
We see this prince
With his grand-ducal robe and embroidered skirt.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-binfeng-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
