      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·豳風·006.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">九罭.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鴻飛遵渚，公歸無所。於女信處。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The wild geese fly only about the islets.
The duke is returning; — is it not to his proper place?
He was stopping with you and me but for a couple of nights.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
