      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·豳風·006.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">九罭.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>是以有袞衣兮，無以我公歸兮，無使我心悲兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Thus have we had the grand-ducal robe among us.
Do not take our duke back to the west;
Do not cause us such sorrow of heart.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
